metadata.description:
Tides represent a renewal of energy. High Tide is indicative of exactly that for this moment in my career as an artist and even more so as an early participant in web3. 

High Tide exists as a stream of consciousness reflecting on my journey this far in web3; things I've observed, people I love, and things I simply don't like.

The record was recorded at Ocean View Beach Park in Norfolk, VA.

lyrics.text:
I look in the mirror and I see digits
Ain’t no I in team ok, but there’s a me isn’t it
I make the most of what’s given
Still there’s some looks that was missing
Prepared a feast for you nigga
& I’m still whipping up fixins
Only cook in the kitchen
Not much to prove but I’m itching
They know the work but don’t mention
What’s a tag to a player in botegga rags
I might be too ambitious,
My every move meticulous
All of my passions was pending 
I put service aside today to put 
pad where the pen is
My spot reserved at the top
Now I’m backing up in it
Don’t hit me acting all friendly
All of your actions are empty
Time to clear the air
Need to stop with the politikin,
Web3 politicians 
nary a pot to piss in
Homie I’m top 2
But I ain’t Scottie Pippen
I’m not role model,
But who they follow isn’t it
All the idea farming
Cuz your engagement slipping
To get to where I’m at in this life
You got to pay a visit
& the operative phrase in that sentence
Is pay a nigga
Yea..come pay a nigga


What you see is a balancing act
Between out performing my peers and panic attacks
Looking down from a position of speaking the facts
And being real past comfort till people detach
I see my toe is on the line cuz I’m passionate
And passion gets hard to handle at times way I package it
Look what I accomplished funny they couldn’t fathom it
Like trend followers trying to tell Fendi what fashion is
My cup overfloweth but they still try to cap on it
FSR on ever coast till they know the acronym
I promise I don’t like it if isn’t immaculate
If you bringing mid, might make you move back a bit
I take the biggest challenge I can find and I tackle it
Ahh man I made it, show them how to cook for themselves then how to plate it
smoking minty pack while Scolla sing affirmations
Cuz Jazii told me only play the game until till you take it
